    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali14-kilavi">itu talaimakaṉāṟ pirivuṇarttappaṭṭa tōḻi, talaimakaṟku, muṉṉai-yiṟ ciṟappai emvayiṟ 
            pārāṭṭiya tellām emvayiṟ piṟanta veṟuppeṉpatu ippoḻutaṟintēṉ, ivvakaippaṭṭa pōkku niṉakku 
            ev-vakaiyāṉ vantateṉa, avaṉ celavaḻuṅkac colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">This is what the confidante, who had been informed by the hero of the separation, said to the hero in order to prevent his going: "this time I have understood that it is dislike that is born on our side of all the words of praise on our part for the superiority of the frontier. In which manner did going that happens in this manner come to you?"</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali14">
                <l>aṇaimaru ḷiṉṟuyi lampaṇait taṭameṉṟōṭ</l>
                <l>ṭuṇaimala reḻiṉīlat tēnteḻiṉ malaruṇkaṇ</l>
                <l>maṇamauvaṉ mukaiyaṉṉa māvīḻvār niraiveṇpaṉ</l>
                <l>maṇanāṟu naṟunutaṉ mārivī ḻiruṅkūnta</l>
                <l>lalarmulai yākat takaṉṟa valkuṟ</l>
                <l>cilanirai vālvaḷaic ceyyā yōveṉap</l>
                <l>palapala kaṭṭurai paṇṭaiyiṟ pārāṭṭi</l>
                <l>yiṉiya colli yiṉṉāṅkup peyarppa</l>
                <l>tiṉiyaṟin tēṉatu tuṉiyā kutalē;</l>
                <l rend="space">poruḷallāṟ poruḷumuṇ ṭōveṉa yāḻaniṉ</l>
                <l>maruḷikoṇ maṭanōkka mayakkappaṭ ṭayarttāyō;</l>
                <l rend="space">kātalā revaṉceypa poruḷillā tārkkeṉa</l>
                <l>vētilār kūṟuñcoṟ poruḷāka matittāyō;</l>
                <l rend="space">cemmaiyi ṉikantorīip poruḷceyvārk kapporu</l>
                <l>ḷimmaiyu maṟumaiyum pakaiyāva taṟiyāyō;</l>
                <l rend="space">ataṉāl,</l>
                <l>emmaiyum poruḷāka matittīttai nammuṇāṅ</l>
                <l>kavavukkai viṭappeṟum poruṭṭiṟat</l>
                <l>tavavukkai viṭuta latumaṉum poruḷē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>            “Broad soft shoulders [like] pretty bamboo, for sweet sleep like on a bed,</l>
<l>blossoming kajal eyes with the eminent grace of graceful blue lotuses as companion blossoms, </l>
<l>white teeth in a straight row desired by [bee-]animals like buds of fragrant wild jasmine,</l>
<l>a fragrant forehead fragrant with scent, dark tresses that are the envy of rain [clouds],</l>
<l>wide hips with a bosom with blooming breasts,</l>
<l>white bangles in few rows, o red one”, so saying,</l>
<l>earlier praising [her] in many many phrases,</l>
<l>speaking sweetly, [your] turning back like this,</l>
<l>now I have understood that that was disgust.</l>
<l rend="space">That there is a wealth apart from wealth,</l>
<l>have you forgotten [that], your confused innocent glance having been confused?</l>
<l rend="space">Thinking “what will lovers do for those who are without wealth?”</l>
<l>did you think that the words spoken by strangers would be wealth?</l>
<l rend="space">Do you not know that to those who make wealth going beyond [and] renouncing </l>
<l>what is right, that wealth with be an enemy in this birth and the next?</l>
<l rend="space">Therefore,</l>
<l rend="space">think of us as wealth: forsaking the longing</l>
<l>for wealth that is obtained when we in our inside</l>
<l>forsake union, that only is wealth. </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
